name: 002 - CHABO
description: Chabo like to collects sign to help the people in need. He always have the pen and paper ready. Why he still use paper on this environmental minded and digital era? Well, he loves that classic-tactile feel, he said it makes him feel little more alive, despite he live from that old li-ion battery energy. And if you curious, Chabo put all the petition he collected below his abdomen part.
